title: MBMBaM 238: Face 2 Face 11: No One Goes Home Alone
description: Live from the Masonic Lodge at the Hollywood Forever Cemetery! Join us as we pitch projects to Tim Allen, discuss the sexual potential of Donny Osmond and hang out with our pal, Drew Davenport.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
